{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Combo Card Clashers</strong></i>, a <strong>roguelike deckbuilder</strong> meets <strong>auto battler</strong> with unique <strong>card combo</strong> battle mechanics. What makes the game unique and different from other deck-building games is the innovative <u><i><strong>Card Combo Grid</strong></i></u> which allows powerful card synergies to be built every turn. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054770/extras/combat_gif_new_EN.gif?t=1728973245\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054770/extras/title-1-en.png?t=1728973245\" />Each turn, you add a card to the combo grid and play all cards in grid. Experiment with the different card synergies and grid placement to unlock powerful effects. Duplicate, modify, and enhance cards to unleash more potential! Build up damage and slay enemies with no-nonsense attacks, blast them with magic spells, or torture them with negative effects - all in one turn!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054770/extras/title-2-en.png?t=1728973245\" />A good team could also lead you to victory. Other than recruiting mercenaries in stores, you could also befriend monsters after combat to become your allies! Their special abilities could just be that trick up your sleeve to win the next fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054770/extras/title-3-en.png?t=1728973245\" />The main game offers three heroes, each with their own unique style and strength. Customize the attributes of each hero and craft their starting deck to maximize their abilities. You can also level up, equip gear, find relics and learn skills to open up new roads to progression.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054770/extras/EN_progression_path.gif?t=1728973245\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054770/extras/title-4-en.png?t=1728973245\" />Embark on a journey, Discover events, buy new cards, upgrade cards, get weapons and gear, recruiting monsters and mercenaries, discover relics, and using strategy to win intense tactical battles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">5 characters! - customize your hero</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">100+ cards &amp; 60 artifacts - build powerful synergies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Free hex maps &amp; procedural generation - new encounters each time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gear and Mercenary Store - You can even recruit monsters to fight for you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3 worlds &amp; 10 levels - Replayability won't be an issue</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>*Combo Card Clashers is part of Erabit's Bud Scheme,\u00a0a space for game creativity &amp; solo devs/small teams to thrive.</i></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Beat a boss","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2054770/57b7f225454203894fa857f01f16354a58766d07.jpg"},{"name":"Rich Hero","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2054770/57299032e69106505f0743af0768ae123377668e.jpg"},{"name":"Combo Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2054770/ed7099486f8be01c2562e7d8b6b35221e5be5ee9.jpg"},{"name":"Monster Slayer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2054770/baa198825d9890cfe6630fd9af522debd2a21d17.jpg"},{"name":"Healer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2054770/fb5598e3934dd88e6b3a444702d1a5a8e1b92bf0.jpg"},{"name":"Enjoying the Story","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2054770/72833745036a7544cf0dad6227d2aba7bb6b6b7b.jpg"},{"name":"Investor","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2054770/7ec08286a3c5a3373e80ec79a38fb3bc2ec7ccec.jpg"},{"name":"Risk Taker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2054770/2e46208b5d132d45b06cf77ea6a29e584c4573ff.jpg"},{"name":"Gear Shopping","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2054770/0316cf2ef52d521b3669e5f908798e21ae91425c.jpg"},{"name":"Card Enthusiast","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2054770/cb845de98571c1aeb2f7bc68df810b1c8b4521df.jpg"}],"total":16},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054770/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728973245","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054770/page.bg.jpg?t=1728973245","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054770/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728973245","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054770/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728973245","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2072300,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Combo Card Clashers</strong></i>, a <strong>roguelike deckbuilder</strong> meets <strong>auto battler</strong> with uniqu